{"type": "article", "id": 25921, "title": "时间迷宫钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-25T06:59:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607140940VDgETNmft6PzUwrR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个名为时间迷宫（<a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_146148520070416&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=ineagxra0100x1tt000DLvqeblqywj2p5&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Ftime-maze-clock-daniel-libeskind-alessi%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alessi.com%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fdetail%2Fdl01-time-maze-wall-clock&amp;title=Time%20Maze%20Clock%20by%20Daniel%20Libeskind%20for%20Alessi%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=Time%20Maze\">Time Maze</a>）的挂钟由建筑师 <a href=\"http://libeskind.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Daniel Libeskind</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.alessi.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">Alessi</a> 所设计。通过奇异的线条组合，时间“既非线形或圆形，而是一个有着抽象联系和趣味互动的迷宫”这一概念得到了充分的体现。整个挂钟由不锈钢制成，红色部分为钟面，12 个小圆点代表了刻度。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140938Tf6oMtYGy47bXm3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.77040111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140938Yk1E8eLyhNmB3IxZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140939pEbZgtUs5vCn7GRT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140939YobATK5h3WMj2Vny.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}